                "id": "9d41bfbaf6ec50241b55b3bf344ea217",
                "type": "task",
                "display_language_text": "It is ok to address **family members** with their respective \"roles\". For example, you can say:",
                "info_text": "This **is** a \"formatted\" info text! neat!",
                "learn_language_text": null,
                "image": null,
                "sound": null,
                "speaker_role": null
              },
              {
                "id": "003382305ca4013597f61ae26c63b12d",
                "type": "phrase",
                "display_language_text": "\"Good morning\", **dear** cousin.",
                "learn_language_text": "((Schöner|*Guten)) \"Morgen\", lieber **Cousin**",
                "info_text": "and your cousin should not be offended",
                "image": null,
                "sound": {
                  "id": "d3572193477785b1bc030cdf61ec777c"
                },
                "speaker_role": "f1"
              },
              {
                "id": "05b1f9a08520098d2cbbb6f343226861",
                "type": "task",
                "display_language_text": "Please type 'yes' or 'äöüß': ((*yes|*äöüß)). We use **the present tense** to talk about \"what is happening right now\". The next answers are 'Sonne' or 'Laterne' and 'Es ist'",
                "learn_language_text": null,
                "info_text": "das Präsens",
                "image": null,
                "sound": null,
                "speaker_role": null
              },
              {
                "id": "658f6323f5380ad34821765803f354b5",
                "type": "phrase",
                "display_language_text": "The \"sun\" is **shining** brightly. It's a beautiful day.",
                "learn_language_text": "Die ((*Sonne|*Laterne)) scheint hell. ((Es ist)) ein schöner Tag.",
                "info_text": "Die **Stadt**. Die \"Straße\". Ich bin \"**Sandra**\".",
                "image": null,
                "sound": {
                  "id": "d3572193477785b1bc030cdf61ec777c"
                },
                "speaker_role": "f1"
              },
              {
                "id": "9647d7e46d7f0df61f45ecfe3cfaaec3",
                "type": "phrase",
                "display_language_text": "I have an \"important question\": **Which** pullover fits (you)?",
                "learn_language_text": "Ich habe eine \"wichtige Frage\": Welch**er** Pullover passt dir?",
                "info_text": null,
                "image": null,
